    <stitle>CAM AIR FOUNDATION BRAKES - BRAKE ADJUSTMENT</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec id="hl0400501">
        <title>BRAKE ADJUSTMENT</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="adjust" graphiccount="0">
            <title>AUTOMATIC SLACK ADJUSTERS</title>
            <para>Automatic slack adjusters maintain proper cam brake chamber stroke adjustment and lining drum
                clearance during the normal service life of brake lining.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>When servicing brakes with spring (PARKING) brake chamber, the chamber must be CAGED. Refer to
                        GROUP 04 - BRAKES in the CTS-5000 Master Service Manual.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Brakes are adjusted with vehicle on floor stands.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
